Note: Only auto attacks can critically strike. Ceruledge's Critical-Hit rate increases at levels 5 and 9.

Charcadet

Evolves At 5

Flame Body

Passive Ability

When Charcadet hits an enemy with an auto attack, Charcadet deals damage around themself with flames. This ability goes on a 4s cd after it's triggered.

Weak Armor

Passive Ability

When the user takes Attack-based damage, Ceruledge's movement speed is increased by 10% for 3s. This effect can stack up to 2 times. If Ceruledge deals damage to enemies with basic attacks or moves, the enemy hit receives a wound. Life energy leaks out of these wounds for 3s, causing damage on hit and then every 0.5s. This effect can stack up to 6 times, each stack after the first adding 50% of the first stack's damage and refreshing the duration of the damage over time. If the effect stacks 6 times on an enemy, that Pokémon takes 15% increased damage from Ceruledge.

100% Atk + 0 x (Level - 1) + 0

7.5% Atk + 0 x (Level - 1) + 0

Attack - Charcadet

Auto Attack

Becomes a boosted attack with every third attack, dealing increased damage.

Attack - Ceruledge

Auto Attack

Becomes a boosted attack every 4 attacks, dealing damage twice. The next basic attack after using a move becomes a boosted attack. After evolving to Ceruledge, basic and boosted attacks have an additional 20% lifesteal.

100% Atk + 0 x (Level - 1) + 0

130% Atk + 0 x (Level - 1) + 0

75% Atk + 0 x (Level - 1) + 0

Lava Plume

Move 1

5.00s Area

Torch the area around the user with an inferno of scarlet flames, dealing damage to enemies hit. The user's next basic attack deals 15% increased damage.

140% Atk + 15 x (Level - 1) + 300

Lava Plume Upgrade Choices

Bitter Blade

6.00s Area

Ceruledge focuses bitter feelings towards the world of the living into a slashing attack. The user recovers HP equals to 40% of the damage dealt with this move. Damage dealt to wild Pokémon only heals for half of the normal amount. Any HP recovered that exceeds the user's max HP is converted into a shield.

242% Atk + 33 x (Level - 1) + 330

Increases the amount of HP recovered to 55% of damage dealt.

Psycho Cut

6.50s Area

Ceruledge launches a blade formed by psychic power in the designated direction, dealing damage and slowing enemies hit by 30% for 3s, and reducing their Defense for 4s. If Ceruledge hits enemies with a basic attack, this move's cooldown is reduced by 0.5s.

160% Atk + 18 x (Level - 1) + 550

0% Atk + 2 x (Level - 1) + 20

Increases the Defense reduction of enemies hit by this move.

0% Atk + 3 x (Level - 1) + 30

Take Down

Move 2

8.00s Dash

Has the user charge recklessly in the designated direction, dealing damage to enemies hit. The user's basic attack speed is increased by 20% for 3s.

140% Atk + 15 x (Level - 1) + 200

Take Down Upgrade Choices

Phantom Force

10.00s Dash

Dash and disappear into darkness, where Ceruledge hides for 1s. While hiding, Ceruledge cannot move. When this move is used again or after 1s has passed, the user appears in the designated direction while slashing around themself, dealing damage that ignores Defense and shields of enemies and applies a 60% slow to them. If this move hits an enemy, this move's cooldown is reduced by 40% of the max cooldown.

125% Atk + 8 x (Level - 1) + 312

Reduces this move's cooldown by 2s.

Flame Charge

8.00s Dash

Ceruledge cloaks themself in flame and charges in the designated direction, dealing damage to enemies hit. Ceruledge's basic attack speed is increased by 30% for 3s after using this move. A maximum of 2 uses can be kept in reserve for this move.

There is a 1 second cooldown between each use, which is reduced with cooldown reduction.

65% Atk + 5 x (Level - 1) + 250

Ceruledge's basic attack speed is instead increased for 5s after using this move.

Revenant Rend

Unite Move

112s 100000 Dash

Unlocks at level 9

Ceruledge charges both of their arm blades gaining unstoppable for 0.5s before slashing through to the designated location faster than the eye can track. Ceruledge leaves enemies hit unable to act for 0.7s and applies a mark to them. After 0.7s, Ceruledge slices marked enemies with three slashing blows. The mark can be cleansed, preventing the damage.

120% Atk + 8 x (Level - 1) + 500

Unite Buffs (6s duration):

30% Movement Speed, 30% CDR, 20% Max HP Shield
